   <body>
      <context>
         <note>Route the battery cables from the adjacent battery
cabinet(s) through the left side panel into the UPS cabinet.</note>
      </context>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Connect the input cables to the input busbars (L1, L2,
L3, N) and to the ground busbar.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <fig>
                  <title>Front View of the UPS Cabinet</title>
                  <image href="../Images/Reality_25_kwupssingle_connectcables_w120mm_0000162095.svg"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Connect the output cables to the output busbars (L1, L2,
L3, N) and to the ground busbar.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Connect the battery cables to the battery busbars (+, –)
and to the ground busbar.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
